## 🔧 **Development & Implementation**

### **Getting Started**
1. **Clone Repository**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/ashish-tandon/AshishTandon.Me.git
   cd AshishTandon.Me
   ```

2. **Install Dependencies**
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```

3. **Run Development Server**
   ```bash
   npm run dev
   ```

4. **View your portfolio**: Open `http://localhost:3000`

### **Available Scripts**
- `npm run dev` - Start development server
- `npm run build` - Build for production
- `npm run start` - Start production server
- `npm run lint` - Run ESLint
- `npm run test` - Run tests
- `npm run type-check` - TypeScript type checking

---

## 📱 **Current Implementation Status**

### **✅ Completed (Phase 1)**
- [x] Next.js 14 project setup with App Router
- [x] TypeScript configuration with strict mode
- [x] Tailwind CSS with custom design system
- [x] Component architecture and structure
- [x] 3D particle network (Three.js)
- [x] Responsive navigation and layout
- [x] All section placeholders
- [x] Dark/light theme toggle
- [x] Smooth animations (Framer Motion)

### **🔄 In Progress (Phase 2)**
- [ ] AI service integration
- [ ] Content management system
- [ ] Dynamic content generation
- [ ] Performance optimization

### **⏳ Planned (Phases 3-7)**
- [ ] Advanced AI features
- [ ] Voice integration
- [ ] Content population
- [ ] Testing and quality assurance
- [ ] Deployment and launch

